==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Preaxial
<hw>Pre*ax"i*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated in front of any transverse axis in the body of an animal;
anterior; cephalic; esp., in front, or on the anterior, or cephalic
(that is, radial or tibial) side of the axis of a limb.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prebend</ent>⟦br⟧
